Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.24,0:08:50.22,eromanga_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur2}繰り返し君と踊った
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:53.85,eromanga_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur2}揺れる景色 道は続く
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.86,0:08:56.47,eromanga_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur2}通り過ぎる風に吹かれ
